# Evidence Directory

This directory stores validation evidence for acceptance criteria.

## Structure

```
/tasks/evidence/
  [feature-id]/
    ac-1/
      test-output.log
      screenshot-*.png
      manual-verification.md
      README.md
    ac-2/
      ...
```

## Evidence Types

- **test-output.log**: Test execution results
- **screenshot-*.png**: Visual proof of functionality
- **logs.txt**: Application logs showing behavior
- **manual-verification.md**: Manual testing results
- **performance.txt**: Performance test results
- **README.md**: Index of all evidence for this AC

## Requirements

Each acceptance criterion must have complete evidence before being marked complete.
